Navigate to collection page: https://tcgpocketcollectiontracker.com/#/collection/8674722716823402

Apply necessary filters to get cards you are after (can take several runs to get all cards downloaded - make sure to run the process script before re-downloading as it requires the .html file)

Right click > Save Page As > Save to .\scripts\card\pocket_download\

Run this script to process the images
python .\scripts\card\process_tcg_pocket_webmp.py .\scripts\card\pocket_download\ --verbose

Manual check - remove any unwanted cards (Megas etc.)

Move the cards in /success into root directory of pocket_download, delete everything else

Run this script to crop and resize cards
python .\scripts\card\resize_and_crop_images.py .\scripts\card\pocket_download\ --crop-x 33 --crop-y 57 --crop-width 320 --crop-height 210 --width 400 --verbose

Manually place cards in their respective directories inside ./scripts/card/pocket_to_move

Run this script to move cards into pokedle_assets repo
python .\scripts\card\move_images.py --input-dir .\scripts\card\pocket_to_move\ --output-dir D:\Github\pokedle_assets\cards --verbose

Commit and Sync pokedle_assets

Run this script to re-build the card manifest file
python .\scripts\card\build_card_manifest_from_dirs.py --input-dir D:\Github\pokedle_assets\cards --output-json .\public\data\card_manifest.json